data.description: If you are looking for a quality built home surrounded by peace and tranquility than look no further! The mature landscaping immediately captures your attention, boasting majestic cypress and oak trees that creates privacy year around. Inside you'll find recently updated flooring, carpet, fixtures and more! Three of the bedrooms are on the first floor along with not one but two living rooms. Your eyes are immediately drawn to all of the natural light provided by the large windows with electric roman shades. Upstairs you'll find a fourth bedroom along with walk-in attic for all your storage needs. Finally in the back you will enjoy a screened in porch, paved patio and a gorgeous view that seems endless! With a roof installed in 2021, updated electrical, plumbing and a new hot water heater with a custom water filtration system you can rest easy for years to come. This home comes with no HOA fees but still has Ogden Park just a brief walk away with optional pool and tennis access. This oasis is just a few minutes from food and shopping at Barclay Point, downtown, the beaches and the medical centers. Something like this doesn't hit the market often. Come see what your future home has to offer today!  Assumable VA loan at 6.125 %
